\pard\tx3401\tx3955\tx5102\tx5669\tx6235\tx6802\li3960\fi-560\ri-4526\ql\qnatural

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
\'a5 New equipment: EQ_HEAT_SHIELD, External heat shielding to make sun-skimming easier; EQ_TARGET_MEMORY, allows the shipcomp to store/recall up to 16 targets.\
\'a5 Improved implementation of radiation damage (very slightly less deadly, applies to NPC ships too).\
\'a5 Implemented scanner un-zoom (press shift-Z).\
\'a5 Allow selection of coincident target systems on the chart screens (click just above or below the system).\
\'a5 Implemented control for ambient light level in planetinfo.plist (<key>ambient_level</key><real>1.0</real>).\
\'a5 Implemented <key>isCarrier</key><true/>|<false/> in shipdata.plist entries.\
\'a5 Implemented <key>rotaing</key><true/>|<false/> in shipdata.plist entries for stations.\
\'a5 Implemented better handling of over-complicated models.\
\'a5 More improemnts to sound code (thanks Ahruman).\
\'a5 Fixed image handling problem (fixes Lave.oxp's moon bug).\
\'a5 Fixed collision/scooping problems (fixes 'ghost escape pod' bug).\
\'a5 Fixed text input problems (fixes 'Commander name change' bug, thanks Winston).\
\'a5 Improvements to missile code: in shipdata.plist <key>missile_role</key> to select missiles fired by the ship, thargons going uncontrolled now properly shuck their target locks.\
\'a5 Optimised lighting routines and aded more respect for the 'Reduced Detail' mode.\
\'a5 Switched to GUSTO (Grand Unified Source Tree for Oolite) for future development.\
\'a5 Many other minor bugfixes and glitch eliminations.\
\
