\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 Version 1.63\
\pard\tx3401\tx3955\tx5102\tx5669\tx6235\tx6802\li3960\fi-560\ri-4526\ql\qnatural

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
\'a5 Bugfix to using zoom key in other chart screens.\
\'a5 Laser vs. Ship collision detection now performed using octrees (more accurate.)\
\'a5 Bug where default volume setting was 'Mute' fixed.\
\'a5 All ship default console graphics are now drawn rather than taken from images.\
\'a5 Hyperspace destination selected is now stored in the save game.\
\'a5 ECM hardened missiles are no longer completely ECM proof (only 90% so.)\
\'a5 Invincible Thargoid bug fixed.\
\'a5 More aggressive data caching at start-up.\
\'a5 Oolite 'strict' implements a non-zero forward velocity when speed is zero (like og. Elite.)\
\'a5 'addShipsWithinRadius:' 'consoleMessage3s:' 'consoleMessage6s:' methods implemented for scripting.\
\'a5 Custom cargopods may be 'pre-filled' in their shipdata.plist entries.\
\'a5 Player ship's model now drawn, permitting views of its external parts!\
\'a5 Minor glitches fixed.\
\'a5 Fuel scoop status indicator added to main display.\
\'a5 Scooping flotsam now uses 'scoop_position' to determine where scooped items disappear into the ship.\
\'a5 Major memory-use problems in AI addressed.\
\'a5 Collision finding majorly overhauled to (crudely) partition space before tracking collisions - a big optimisation.\
